### Login as CUSTOMER (stores cookies in REST client session)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.user@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Get customer orders (expected 200; items populated if seed sample orders exist for this user)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/orders

### Get one customer order — replace ORDER_ID with an id from the list response (expected 200 or 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/orders/ORDER_ID

### Logout customer session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/logout

### Get customer orders after logout (expected 401)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/orders

### Login as VENDOR-only account
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vendor.user@example.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!"
}

### Get customer orders as non-customer role (expected 403)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/customer/orders
